mistral.reason: First Look Studios was an American independent film distributor that specialized in home video releases of films and television series. However, Quicksand (2003 film) was a British-French-German co-produced crime thriller film. Therefore, it was not distributed by First Look Studios as the company's focus was primarily on American independent films.
